Class ExamResult

java.lang.Object
com.panotify.model.ExamResult
public class ExamResult extends Object
Represents the result of a student's exam attempt in the PaNotify system. Contains information about the exam, student, scores, and submission status.
Version:
1.0
Author:
PaNotify Team
